NEWS information for package RxpsG
Exploratory and Processing for XPS Spectra
by Giorgio Speranza

==> RxpsG version 3.1 derived from version 2.3-2 but now directly using tcltk.
Libraries gWidgets2, gWidgets2tcltk, memoise are no more necessary reducing 
the package requirements. 
The software was controlled but still some bugs could be present: contact 
speranza@fbk.eu for problems.  

==> Previous version RxpsG 2.3-2
Number of bugs fixed, more robust code for working in Windows and Linux operating systems
Complete documentation of the S4-classes and methods, and of all the functions.


